    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped onion </strong>to the dish with the <strong>tomato wedges </strong>and <strong>crushed garlic</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and stir everything together</p>",
