    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>bay leaf<span class=\"text-danger\">[ves] </span></strong>and 1/2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> to the pot with 600ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[800ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Stir in the <strong>red wine stock</strong>,<strong> beef stock mix </strong>and <strong>tortiglioni </strong>and<strong> </strong>give everything a good mix up</p><p>Nestle the pasta into the water as much as you can, then stir everything together and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
